&lt;h2 id="workflow-of-ai-tools-in-business-operations"&gt;Workflow of AI Tools in Business Operations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Understanding how AI tools fit into your business operations can be visualized as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
